                     <interp inst="t18240603-102-off537" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240603-102-off537" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240603-102-cd538" type="crimeDate">12th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240603-102-off537 t18240603-102-cd538"></join>, a parcel, containing two rings, value 50 s.; a book, value 20 s.; a shift, value 10 s.; a bed-gown, value 4 s.; a petticoat, value 1 s., and a frill, value 3 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18240603-102-victim877" type="victimName">
                           Hannah Margaret 
                           Elbon
